list.item:
Clean your child’s diaper area after each diaper change. Gently wipe the diaper area from the front to back using warm (
not hot
) water. You may also use a mild soap. Rinse the diaper area well. Pat dry with a soft towel.

text.paragraph:
Store at 15oC (77oF); 
excursions permitted to 25oC -30oC 
(59oF -86oF).
